  <brief_title>Chidamide Plus Chemotherapy in the Treatment of Peripheral T-cell Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Prospective, Single-arm, Open Label Phase II Study of Chidamide Combined With Chemotherapy in the Treatment of Peripheral T Cell Lymphoma</official_title>
