  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single arm, prospective trial to evaluate the efficacy and safety of Chidamide in
      combination with previous chemotherapy in peripheral T cell lymphoma patients who did not
      achieve complete response after 3 cycles of chemotherapy in interim evaluation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
